            "subtype": "ability",
            "success": "The target is enfeebled 1 for 1 round.",
            "text": "The attic whisperer siphons the breath from living creatures, sapping their strength. A living creature hit by a jaws Strike must attempt a DC 21 Fortitude save.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
